### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE Experiment (
   experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   experiment_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
   start_date DATE,
   end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Study (
   study_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   study_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
   study_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Sample (
   sample_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   experiment_id INT,
   sample_type VARCHAR(50),
   collection_date DATE,
   FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES Experiment(experiment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE SequencingData (
   data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   sample_id INT,
   sequencing_date DATE,
   raw_data BYTEA,
   FOREIGN KEY (sample_id) REFERENCES Sample(sample_id)
);

### STATEMENT

DELETE FROM SequencingData WHERE sample_id IN (SELECT sample_id FROM Sample WHERE experiment_id IN (SELECT experiment_id FROM Experiment WHERE start_date < '2022-01-01'))
